main event: A civilian reported a stationary white object in the sky resembling the size of a dime observed for two minutes.
interesting points: The object was at a 30 degree elevation for the entire observation duration., The report was generated from a Project Blue Book record card., The object remained stationary and did not move during the observation., The report concluded that the scientific data and analysis could not provide a satisfactory explanation., There were no additional reports or data filed regarding the sighting.
sighted object: a white object the size of a dime
